</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_176" id="86v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Lienhart<ex>en</ex></expan>, grafen und
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czü Kastel </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als ir uns <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des Rötleins,
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> armen mannes,
                            <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>; <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir Wölflein Glacz,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, besant und cze rede gesaczt und der sprichet
                        aber, daz er die sache auf <expan>geistliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab <expan>angevange<ex>n</ex></expan>, die
                        weil <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Rötlein <add>dannoch</add>
<expan>hint<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>burgg<ex>ra</ex>f<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>johans<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>gesezze<ex>n</ex></expan> sey; und
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burgg<ex>ra</ex>fen</expan>, bede <expan>hofmeist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> in geredt, daz er den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vorlangst beczalt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> solt. Doch so
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        willen mit dem <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> geredt, daz er sprichet, sey
                        es, daz ir im <expan>hiczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                        <app><note><q type="date"><expan>ost<ex>er</ex>n</expan></q>07.04.1409</note></app> rechtens <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Rötlein helffet, so wöll er das vor ew
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> nemen. Und wenn im das recht vollgee,
                        so wöll er die klag auf <expan>geistliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> abetün <add>und auch sein klag <add>die
                                weil</add> also besteen <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> und in
                                    <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> czeit nicht
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>rer</expan>
<expan>treib<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>; und er hab in auf das lantgericht
                        nicht geladen, wo etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii <expan>ciner<ex>um</ex></expan> ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
